{"about_the_game":"Aery \u2013 Heaven &amp; Hell is a story-driven 3D flight exploration game in which you control a flying god-like creature on its abstract journey though the passions and fears of the human race. On its adventure to learn more about the humans you will pass through many personal heavens and hells of certain individuals. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game is a peaceful, philosophical and relaxing experience and offers an interesting meta story, the sensation of flying and enjoyable non-violent gameplay to relax after a day filled with stress and hassle. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhile you progress through the story you will be able to see into the minds of different humans and realize what moves them forward, what hold them back and what they are reaching for.  You will be able to explore these abstractly represented and sometimes even surreal thoughts as a small bird like creature that can move freely in each world. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis story-driven game is non-violent so that you can enjoy the intuitive and relaxing gameplay in 14 giant different stages that are waiting to be explored.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Act 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2142640/9cbc6dc929286f455ba1b8667e1f7312fe0f6be2.jpg"},{"name":"Act 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2142640/9cbc6dc929286f455ba1b8667e1f7312fe0f6be2.jpg"},{"name":"Act 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2142640/9cbc6dc929286f455ba1b8667e1f7312fe0f6be2.jpg"},{"name":"Act 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2142640/9cbc6dc929286f455ba1b8667e1f7312fe0f6be2.jpg"},{"name":"Act 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2142640/9cbc6dc929286f455ba1b8667e1f7312fe0f6be2.jpg"},{"name":"Act 6","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2142640/9cbc6dc92928